HEADWORD: Adjuster
<hw>Ad*just"er</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who, or that which, adjusts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>an insurance agent who examines claims against
personal or property damage insurance policies and makes estimates and
recommendations regarding the amount which should be paid to the
policyholder.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

